(69, 157960, 'DJVE de subproducto de soja por 54 mil toneladas', '2016-05-11 13:44:00', 'http://www.fyo.com/sites/default/files/djve-granos_43.png', 'http://www.fyo.com/noticia/157960/djve-subproducto-soja-54-mil-toneladas', 'Mercado de granos', 'También se presentaron DJVE de aceite de soja por 7 mil toneladas, girasol por 56 toneladas, maíz por 15 mil toneladas, soja por 586 toneladas y trigo pan por 290.', ' <table style="color: #222222; font-size: 12.8px; width: 717px;" border="0" cellpadding="0"><colgroup><col width="96" /><col span="3" width="80" /><col width="221" /></colgroup><tbody><tr style="height: 26.25pt;"><td style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; width: 72pt; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-right-color: gray; border-top-color: gray; border-bottom-color: gray; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-top: 1px; background: #a6a6a6;" width="96">GRANOS</td>\n<td style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; width: 60pt; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-right-color: gray; border-top-color: gray; border-bottom-color: gray; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-top: 1px; background: #a6a6a6;" width="80">TN</td>\n<td style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; width: 60pt; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-right-color: gray; border-top-color: gray; border-bottom-color: gray; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-top: 1px; background: #a6a6a6;" width="80">Campaña</td>\n<td style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; width: 60pt; font-size: 10pt; text-align: center; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-right-color: gray; border-top-color: gray; border-bottom-color: gray; padding-left: 1px; padding-right: 1px; padding-top: 1px; background: #a6a6a6;" width="80">O